casebody.data:
Wednesday, December 16, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

92-218. State ex rel. Barker v. Etheridge.

In Mandamus. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents and would issue a show cause order why the cause should not be dismissed.
